-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/rigby-on-addictive-video-games-rivlin-on-budget-audio.html
Scott Rigby, president of Immersyve 
Inc., talks with Kathleen Hays about the Electronic 
Entertainment Expo and his new book, "Glued to Games: How Video 
Games Draw Us In and Hold Us Spellbound." Alice Rivlin, former 
vice chairman of the Federal Reserve and founding director of 
the Congressional Budget Office, talks with Kathleen Hays about 
the U.S. budget and the debt ceiling.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 25:41
 